highlights.text: Jin has the most spots on Top Songs Singapore. “Don’t Say You Love Me” is the highest at #1.
“你，好不好？ - TVBS連續劇【遺憾拼圖】片尾曲” by Eric Chou has been on Top Songs Singapore the longest, at 3186 days straight.
“One Last Time” by Ariana Grande is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Singapore, up 33 spots at #101.
